                    | RebelFoods is just awesome! I just launched a startup which leaves me with no time for cooking, so
                    | Omnifood is a life-saver. Now that I got used to it, I couldn't live without my daily meals!
    section#plans
        .plans-header
            h2 START EATING HEALTHY TODAY
            hr
        .plans-content
            .plan-box
                .box-head
                    h3 PREMIUM
                    h2 399$ / month
                    p That’s only 13.30$ per meal
                .box-content
                    p
                        i.fa-solid.fa-check
                        | 1 meal every day
                    p
                        i.fa-solid.fa-check
                        | Order 24/7
                    p
                        i.fa-solid.fa-check
                        | Access to newest creations
                    p
                        i.fa-solid.fa-check
                        | Free delivery
                .box-footer
                    if name
                        a.book.btn(href='/plans') Buy now
                    else
                        a.book.btn(href='/login') Sign up now        
